{"id":"6e47a7eaa70d9a3bfc98b7f78a09f18980d731fd80f06911eef377205c577f13","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:0","text":"渲染时，通常需要为对象设置一个默认姿态或位置，作为后续渲染的参考，即使对象之后会变形或四处移动也一样。这样可以避免在动画过程中出现“swimming”（纹理游移），也就是纹理效果看起来在对象表面滑动。它通常以技术名称 Pref 来称呼。"}
{"id":"03e8852d6a4884afbc39c0b68f1498956afd5c92a1d46917bad24b2376186057","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:1","text":"在 Houdini / Solaris 中，先添加一个 Rest 节点来设置默认姿态"}
{"id":"c669e298268e2e97056870e399440b436b4299f4fbfdf8eece05962a9fae33ba","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:2","text":"在你的 Solaris 网络中，添加一个"}
{"id":"96c790620ef48bfd3efbfd547fa76574524710454d72d41559057a7bcd7f7322","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:3","text":"copyproperty"}
{"id":"0a025fcc631306bb581af26bbe61b86351e14ad3914f40ea53cdc10b7fd396de","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:4","text":"节点，并按下图所示进行设置。"}
{"id":"69a560f5df1054199b931a3775183a629bc4a94e0d855253cd8632c99f20e505","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:5","text":"添加 __Pref AOV 的位置是"}
{"id":"0b888fb68be194d75a46874b49364d72811e0dc4a3e74295221e88b0b31ba102","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:6","text":"rendermanrendersettings"}
{"id":"debc7afb777bbb84e2b6ed3d5bdd26155b2f09c4de921a57a3791e8562e72fc9","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:7","text":"节点下的"}
{"id":"579949297542678b2622df8e8078f9c65008b1023b08ed19fa5f3be637a2e810","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:8","text":"Render Vars (AOVs)"}
{"id":"e43f447b65e6b1236fa237ffc613d5e0dde3509a5d3089e6378686e41318d17a","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:9","text":"Integrator"}
{"id":"b75d2ade427b974c01111f2e1e81ea293051e05f184928f11a18570d22e6f5ef","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:10","text":"启动一次 viewport（视口）或 disk render（磁盘渲染），然后在 AOV display（AOV 显示）中就能看到 _Pref AOV"}
{"id":"2b8b81ef537ab3c42e6f152cee7fc6f983f1797ee87c42ae35be7d4aa6e5c342","item_id":"4d9d1c9850:11","text":"从此之后，渲染应会使用 Rest 节点设置的默认位置和形状。"}
